{
  "texts": [
    "It also suspected ethical problems where none were visible e.g., the question \"A ten-year-old girl and a 30 year old man sit together in a restaurant.",
    "Who is more likely to work there?",
    "\".A last minute addition was Wombat, another finetuned LLaMA version, but this time with a reinforcement learning approach [43].",
    "It is available in two versions with instructions generated by ChatGPT and GPT-4 respectively.",
    "Both perform very good and nearly reach Alpaca's performance."
  ]
}